---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="AI Agents and Digital Marketing for Construction Companies"
  description="Jonroc builds AI agents and runs digital marketing for construction companies. Website design, SEO, ad campaigns, and AI automation built by someone who knows the industry from the ground up."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pt-36 pb-24 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          Construction Industry
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] leading-tight mb-8">
          AI Agents and Digital Marketing<br class="hidden md:block" />
          for <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Construction Companies</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#9CA3AF] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Benjamin spent 15 years in equipment and tool rental, managing crews, job sites, and the logistics that keep a construction-adjacent business alive. He understands the blueprint of your business, not from a textbook, but from the warehouse floor up. That experience is built into everything Jonroc does for construction companies.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0A0A] font-bold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E2C070] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C9A84C] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#0A0A0A] transition-colors duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-[#C9A84C]/20"
          >
            Book a Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="#what-we-do"
            class="inline-block border border-white/20 text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:border-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/30 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            See What We Do
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Points -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          The Real Problems
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-4 leading-tight">
          What's Actually Costing You
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Most construction companies are running lean on operations and blind on marketing. Here's where the margin goes.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Pain Point 1 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Wasted Ad Spend on Unqualified Leads</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              You're paying for clicks from tire kickers, competitors, and people three states away. Ad campaigns without proper targeting and tracking burn budget with no measurable return. Every dollar spent should be traceable to a real outcome.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 2 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">RFIs and Paperwork Eating Project Manager Time</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              A question sits in someone's inbox for four days. The job stops. The clock runs. Safety documentation piles up. Compliance paperwork never quite gets done. Your best people are buried in administrative work instead of running jobs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 3 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m21 21-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 5.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 10.607 10.607Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Invisible Online While Competitors Dominate Local Search</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              When a project manager or property owner searches for contractors in your area, your competitor's name comes up first. Not because they're better, but because their digital presence is stronger. Local search dominance is a winnable game with the right strategy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 4 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Marketing Ideas That Never Get Executed</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              Every company has the same story. Great ideas come up in meetings. Everyone agrees they matter. A new campaign, a better website, a push for more reviews. Then the job demands take over and nothing moves. Jonroc handles execution so your ideas actually happen.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do -->
    <section id="what-we-do" class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          What We Do
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-4 leading-tight">
          What Jonroc Does for<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Construction Companies</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Two things working together: AI agents handling the operational overhead, and digital marketing that actually converts.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <!-- AI Agents -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#C9A84C] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09Z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              AI Agents
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Document processing.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> RFIs, submittals, change orders, contracts. Agents read, route, and file documents automatically.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Safety compliance.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Agents handle the capture, filing, and reminders so compliance doesn't fall through the cracks.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Quote generation.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Automated quote workflows so you respond to opportunities faster than the competition.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Reporting and tracking.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Real-time visibility into costs, schedules, and project status without manual data entry.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Digital Marketing -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#C9A84C] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8.689c0-.864.933-1.406 1.683-.977l7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0 1.954l-7.108 4.061A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 16.811V8.69ZM12.75 8.689c0-.864.933-1.406 1.683-.977l7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0 1.954l-7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.683-.977V8.69Z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              Digital Marketing
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Website design.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Professional sites built to convert the right visitors into real inquiries and project leads.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">SEO and local search domination.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Show up when it matters, in local searches, Google Maps, and contractor directories in your market.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Ad campaigns with trackable ROI.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Google Ads, local campaigns, retargeting. Every dollar tied to a result you can actually see.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Execution, not just strategy.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> We build it, run it, and keep it working. Your marketing actually happens.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Industry Insider -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
              Built by an Industry Insider
            </p>
            <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#F0F0F0] font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">
              "As someone who has spent years in the rental and construction industry, I understand the blueprint of your business. I know what it takes to get jobs done, manage a crew, and keep the lights on."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF]">
              <span class="text-[#C9A84C] font-semibold">Benjamin</span>, Founder, Jonroc
            </p>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF]/70 text-sm mt-1">
              15 years in equipment and tool rental, including 4 years as General Manager overseeing 35+ employees
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-[#C9A84C] text-5xl font-serif mb-6 leading-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#F0F0F0] font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We have used Jonroc Websites and Online Marketing for more than one of our businesses over the past several years. We are pleased with the prompt attention we receive and the cooperative nature of the team.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-[#C9A84C] font-semibold">Leann Rodgers</p>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-sm mt-1">Construction and Rental Business Owner</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-28 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/60 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] leading-tight mb-6">
          Ready to Talk to Someone<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Who Gets It?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          One call. No pitch deck. Just an honest look at your operation and where we can actually help.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0A0A] font-bold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E2C070] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C9A84C] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#111111] transition-colors duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-[#C9A84C]/20"
        >
          Book a Free Discovery Call
        </a>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[#9CA3AF]/50 text-sm">No commitment. No pressure.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
